features: Value for Money: No more buying costly Rubber Door Stop Wedge to hold your door open. Get Affixers’ improved version which is heavier, handy and more flexible compared to other plastic Door Stoppers for Floor you'll see at the market

Sturdy & Durable Material: Our Door Wedges indoors are made up of strong yet flexible, thick and durable rubber, not easy to deform, and are made to last for many years to come. They provide optimum friction to keep the door deadbolt

Enhanced & Reinforced: Our Doorstop relies on a unique sloped and hollow design to create vacuum with the floor, thus stop door slamming. The outdoor door stop fit under most door gaps, and will withstand daily use without cracking apart

Ideal for Multiple Surfaces: The material of our Door Stops indoors is suitable for all kind of surfaces such as wood, cement, vinyl, tile, or carpet. Affixers’ modern and strongest Door Stopper work on any floor, the rougher the ground, the stronger the grip of the door holder

Prevent Injuries & Accidents: Doors may become a serious issue for pet's and children’s safety, when it’s windy outside and a sudden gust comes along and shuts the door may cause painful injuries. Fortunately, our Heavy Duty patio door stop enables your household to avoid these accidents and injuries
description: Product Description Affixers Door Stops Hold the Door at Any Position Slim and Stylish Door Stop Holds the Door for A Hush Baby Nap Affixers Door Stops are made of high-quality rubber and work well on all surfaces. Effortless to use. Just place the wedge on the floor, push it under your door till it's firmly in place and hold your door at any angle. Keep fresh air circulating in your room and prevent any accidental closures. Patented Design Prevents Moving the Door in Both Direction Maintains A Strong Hold on All Surfaces The Door Stop is made of quality rubber that can hold onto any surface and won't slip as you move the door. It will keep the door in place and prevent it from moving to any side. Made Of Strong Yet Flexible Rubber That Won't Deform The rubber used in the construction is durable yet flexible. You won't have to worry about any deformations developing over time. Conveniently place it on any surface and under any door. Use Your Feet to Place/Remove It Easily The door stops require no installation. Just push them under your door with your feet or hand and press them for a firm grip. To remove it, push the door in the opposite direction. It doesn't get easier than that! Rubber Door Stopper Won't Leave Any Marks on Any Floor Type Won't Leave Any Marks on Your Floor Doorstops can be a problem if they cause marks on your floors or easily scrap. Use door stops and forget about these marks or scraps. You can use them on any surface and during any season, and they won't leave any marks on your floor. Won't Lose Their Shape Over Time Made of heavy-duty rubber, these door stops will not lose their shape over time. So, no matter how long you place them under your door, they won't scrap. Holds The Door in Place Firmly to Prevent Any Movement The door stops will hold your door firmly in place and prevent them from moving at any angle. As a result, you won't have to deal with any banging keeping your home's environment as peaceful as ever. Affixers Door Stops Specifications
